title: Was an Australian teenager attacked by fleshy sea bugs?
subtitle: It is likely that a 16-year-old child was bitten by an unusually large number of sea fleas - not lice, as originally mentioned.
author: Alex Kasprak
vclaim: An Australian teenager was taken to hospital with blood flowing from his feet after he was attacked by "sea lice" after he wet his feet in the water at Melbourne Beach.
